# Consolidates duplicate author identities so `git log`/`git shortlog` show one
# entry per contributor. Format:
#   Canonical Name <canonical-email> <other-commit-email>
# Note: a .mailmap only changes how history is *displayed*; it does not rewrite
# the commits themselves. To remove contributor emails from history entirely,
# a history rewrite (e.g. squash to a fresh initial commit) is required.
